---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import personalData from '../data/personal.json';

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
const title = `Privacy | ${personalData.name}`;

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title={title} description={`Informativa privacy del portfolio di ${personalData.name}.`}>
  <main id="main-content" class="policy-page">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl py-24">
      <a href={`${base}`} class="back-link">
        <span data-lang="it">← Torna al portfolio</span>
        <span data-lang="en">← Back to portfolio</span>
      </a>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2 gradient-text">
        <span data-lang="it">Informativa privacy</span>
        <span data-lang="en">Privacy policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-12">
        <span data-lang="it">Ultimo aggiornamento: gennaio {currentYear}</span>
        <span data-lang="en">Last updated: January {currentYear}</span>
      </p>

      <div class="prose-section">
        <h2>
          <span data-lang="it">1. Informazioni raccolte</span>
          <span data-lang="en">1. Information We Collect</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="it">
            Questo è un sito portfolio statico. Raccogliamo solo le informazioni che invii
            volontariamente tramite il modulo di contatto: nome, email e messaggio.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en">
            This is a static portfolio website. We collect only information you voluntarily provide
            through the contact form: your name, email address, and message content.
          </span>
        </p>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="it">
            Non usiamo cookie, pixel di tracciamento o script di analytics. Non raccogliamo indirizzi
            IP né dati di navigazione.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en">
            We do not use cookies, tracking pixels, or analytics scripts. We do not collect IP
            addresses or browsing behaviour.
          </span>
        </p>

        <h2>
          <span data-lang="it">2. Come usiamo le informazioni</span>
          <span data-lang="en">2. How We Use Your Information</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="it">
            Le informazioni inviate tramite il modulo di contatto servono solo a rispondere alla tua
            richiesta. Le submission sono processate da
            <a href="https://web3forms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Web3Forms</a> e si
            applica la loro
            <a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">informativa privacy</a>.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en">
            Information submitted via the contact form is used solely to respond to your inquiry.
            Contact form submissions are processed by
            <a href="https://web3forms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Web3Forms</a> — their
            <a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">privacy policy</a>
            governs that data.
          </span>
        </p>

        <h2>
          <span data-lang="it">3. Servizi di terze parti</span>
          <span data-lang="en">3. Third-Party Services</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="it">Il sito carica risorse dai seguenti servizi di terze parti:</span>
          <span data-lang="en">This site loads resources from the following third-party services:</span>
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <span data-lang="it">
              <strong>Google Fonts</strong> — tipografia (Inter). I font vengono cacheati localmente in fase di build e serviti da questo dominio. Le richieste raggiungono <code>fonts.googleapis.com</code> solo se la cache locale non può essere costruita.
            </span>
            <span data-lang="en">
              <strong>Google Fonts</strong> — typography (Inter). Font files are cached locally at build
              time and served from this domain. Requests reach <code>fonts.googleapis.com</code> only if
              the local cache could not be built (e.g. no network access during the build).
            </span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span data-lang="it">
              <strong>Iconify</strong> — icone social caricate su richiesta da <code>api.iconify.design</code>.
            </span>
            <span data-lang="en">
              <strong>Iconify</strong> — social icons loaded on demand from <code>api.iconify.design</code>.
            </span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span data-lang="it"><strong>Web3Forms</strong> — endpoint per il modulo di contatto.</span>
            <span data-lang="en"><strong>Web3Forms</strong> — contact form submission endpoint.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="it">
            Ognuno di questi servizi può registrare il tuo indirizzo IP come parte del normale
            funzionamento. Consulta le rispettive privacy policy per i dettagli.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en">
            Each of these services may log your IP address as part of normal server operation. Please
            review their respective privacy policies for details.
          </span>
        </p>

        <h2>
          <span data-lang="it">4. Conservazione dei dati</span>
          <span data-lang="en">4. Data Retention</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="it">
            Non conserviamo dati personali sui nostri server. I dati del modulo di contatto sono
            conservati da Web3Forms secondo la loro policy.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en">
            We do not store any personal data on our own servers. Contact form data is retained by
            Web3Forms per their policy.
          </span>
        </p>

        <h2>
          <span data-lang="it">5. I tuoi diritti</span>
          <span data-lang="en">5. Your Rights</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="it">
            Puoi richiedere la cancellazione di qualsiasi invio del modulo contattando
            <a href={`mailto:${personalData.email}`}>{personalData.email}</a>.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en">
            You may request deletion of any contact form submission by emailing
            <a href={`mailto:${personalData.email}`}>{personalData.email}</a>.
          </span>
        </p>

        <h2>
          <span data-lang="it">6. Modifiche a questa informativa</span>
          <span data-lang="en">6. Changes to This Policy</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="it">
            Questa informativa può essere aggiornata periodicamente. La data in alto riflette la
            revisione più recente.
          </span>
          <span data-lang="en">
            This policy may be updated periodically. The date at the top of this page reflects the
            most recent revision.
          </span>
        </p>

        <h2>
          <span data-lang="it">7. Contatti</span>
          <span data-lang="en">7. Contact</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="it">Domande sulla privacy? Scrivi a </span>
          <span data-lang="en">Privacy questions? Reach out at </span>
          <a href={`mailto:${personalData.email}`}>{personalData.email}</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy-page {
    background-color: var(--bg);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .prose-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }
  .prose-section p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-section ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-section li {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .prose-section a {
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }
  .prose-section a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .prose-section code {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.875em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
